I love this old movie. I saw it as a kid in 1958. The reason the name is a misnomer is because it was changed. The original name was simply "The Spider" and the trailer called it 50 tons of terror. I do remember being totally terrified of this and did not want to sleep in the dark that night. 

I am glad to have finally found it.
